window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Rory Miller's <i>Facing Violence: Preparing for the Unexpected</i> includes seven elements that must be addressed to bring self-defense training to something approaching complete. These elements are: legal and ethical implications, violence dynamics, avoidance, counter-ambush, breaking the freeze, the fight itself, and the aftermath. Training that dismisses any of these areas leaves you vulnerable. </p>"; 
